snippet.title: Spook Squad enters Early Access
snippet.description:
Fuzz Force: Spook Squad is now on Steam Early Access.
Now is the time for you to join in and have your say in development and shape how the game turns out.
Pick up the game on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1422190
